   Before you send bug reports, make sure you have read and understood
this document entirely. It may cover certain aspects you have missed so
far and solve your problem, thus eliminating the need to contact the
author.

   If you send bug reports, do state program and triton version, maybe
include Segtracker, TNT or Enforcer information, your hardware
configuration, what tools, patches and hacks you are using.

   ---------- Footnotes ----------

   (1)  do not send mail bombs :-)


